@startuml
title Activity Diagram FR-13: Maintenance / OOS

|Lab Asset Manager|
start
:Reach assets list;
:Select a hardware asset;

|Dashboard|
:Display asset info;

|Lab Asset Manager|
:Choose status;

if (Set OOS or Available?) then (Set Out of Service)
    |Dashboard|
    :Update asset status to OOS;
    |Lab Asset Manager|
    :Input reason and expected return date;
    |Dashboard|
    :Remove from available assets list;
    :Display OOS banner on asset info page;
    |Lab Asset Manager|
    :Confirm asset is OOS;
    :Reach available assets list;
    :Confirm asset not in available list;
    |Lab Asset Manager|
    :Navigate to ALL assets list;
    :Select the asset;
    |Dashboard|
    :Display asset details with Out of Service status;
    stop
else (Set Available)
    |Dashboard|
        if (Current status is OOS?) then (yes)
            :Update asset to Available;
            :Add to available assets list;
            :Update asset info page;
            |Lab Asset Manager|
            :Confirm Available status;
            :Navigate to available assets list;
            :Verify asset appears in available list;
            |Lab Asset Manager|
            :Select the asset;
            |Dashboard|
            :Display asset details with Available status;
            stop
        else (no)
            :Display error: Asset is already available;
            stop
    endif
endif

@enduml


